duck: Reading (computer) - Reading is an action performed by computers, to acquire data from a source and place it into their volatile memory for processing.
Readability - Readability can mean how easy it is to read and to make sense of a text.
Human-readable - A human-readable medium or human-readable format is a representation of data or information that can be naturally read by humans.
readable definition: able to be read easily.
